780
01:02:53,102 --> 01:02:55,138
♪I wonder if you'll ever get lost.

781
01:02:55,238 --> 01:02:56,873
♪That's okay.

782
01:02:56,973 --> 01:02:58,374
♪No need to be changed.

783
01:02:58,474 --> 01:03:01,110
♪Let's throw away what we really didn't need,

784
01:03:01,210 --> 01:03:05,281
♪the sofa, and the books too.

785
01:03:05,381 --> 01:03:07,016
♪That's okay.

786
01:03:07,116 --> 01:03:12,388
♪Is there a big light that keeps
illuminating your night?

787
01:03:12,488 --> 01:03:15,024
♪I wonder if you're still going.

788
01:03:15,124 --> 01:03:16,826
♪That's okay.

789
01:03:16,926 --> 01:03:18,294
♪No need to be changed.

790
01:03:18,394 --> 01:03:21,097
♪When you have read all,

791
01:03:21,197 --> 01:03:24,133
♪please open your eyes.

792
01:03:31,340 --> 01:03:36,179
♪Let's throw away this book
and go out to the town.

793
01:03:36,279 --> 01:03:47,423
♪～

794
01:03:59,836 --> 01:04:06,976
