795
01:04:07,076 --> 01:04:08,344
I hear wings.

796
01:04:08,444 --> 01:04:11,180
Something flies in through
the open window.

797
01:04:11,280 --> 01:04:14,951
(Sound of insect wings)

798
01:04:19,522 --> 01:04:21,057
It's a flying insect.

799
01:04:21,157 --> 01:04:25,461
Perhaps a kind of stag beetle.
It has two short pincers.

800
01:04:39,075 --> 01:04:42,912
♪～(Piano Sonata 」Moonlight」)

801
01:04:44,347 --> 01:04:47,416
I rush to get my sketchbook.

802
01:04:52,154 --> 01:04:54,624
One night, I see a chameleon.

803
01:04:54,924 --> 01:04:58,427
As I play the piano,
I watch its tail hanging from
