01:27:50,331 --> 01:27:57,739
(Phone ringing)

988
01:27:59,941 --> 01:28:03,845
Did you see the picture I sent?

989
01:28:04,846 --> 01:28:06,681
What did you think?

990
01:28:08,283 --> 01:28:12,820
Actually, I tried drawing
