993
01:28:19,027 --> 01:28:23,064
This series of pictures
is called 」Dancing Animals.」

994
01:28:23,364 --> 01:28:26,401
I think
they've turned out really interesting.

995
01:28:26,668 --> 01:28:27,835
Yeah.

996
01:28:28,636 --> 01:28:29,871
Uh-huh.

997
01:28:30,071 --> 01:28:32,540
Oh, uh...

998
01:28:32,640 --> 01:28:36,311
Canary, rabbit, chameleon,

999
01:28:36,411 --> 01:28:40,915
owl, leaf beetle, frog, bat,

1000
01:28:41,649 --> 01:28:44,052
and the deer.

1001
01:28:44,786 --> 01:28:49,991
Huh? No, seriously.
I was visited by a deer. A stag.

1002
01:28:52,627 --> 01:28:57,465
Yeah, I get it. It sounds unbelievable.

1003
01:28:57,799 --> 01:29:00,968
Yes, the first one is of a human...

1004
01:29:01,069 --> 01:29:04,572
I mean, humans are animals too,
so I just had to draw it.

1005
01:29:04,672 --> 01:29:07,041
The motif?

1006
01:29:07,775 --> 01:29:09,744
Uh, well...

1007
01:29:10,578 --> 01:29:11,746
Yeah?

1008
01:29:12,080 --> 01:29:15,750
Huh? An exhibition?

1009
01:29:17,352 --> 01:29:18,786
Where?

1010
01:29:20,388 --> 01:29:22,623
Oh, there.

1011
01:29:22,857 --> 01:29:25,793
Are you sure? I mean...

1012
01:29:26,928 --> 01:29:29,831
Wait. I'll do it.

1013
01:29:30,832 --> 01:29:33,768
This is a great chance. Sure.

1014
01:29:33,868 --> 01:29:36,437
This makes me so happy. Thank you.

1015
01:29:36,671 --> 01:29:40,441
I'll prep what I've drawn before
so they can be displayed too.

1016
01:29:40,541 --> 01:29:45,680
Sure. Let's meet so we can
talk things over face-to-face.

1017
01:29:46,013 --> 01:29:49,650
Okay. See you later.

1018
01:29:57,058 --> 01:29:59,794
This is a golden opportunity.

1019
